body_html: I must apologize to you guys, because it seems that since davidzchen's patch, the build is actually working without hacking. I apparently forgot a git-pull and used an older version. Sorry about the rant. I appreciate all of your work and thanks to you (the devs) in particular and google in general for open-sourcing such a great tool.
